He has held the title of Grenada Calypso Monarch a record nine times in 1987, 1988, 1990, 1991, 1992, 1995, 2004, 2014 and again in 2015, meaning that he holds the most crowns in comparison to anyone else in Grenada Calypso.
In 1998, he was appointed as a Member of The Order of the British Empire.
Ajamu now has a band based in Brooklyn.
In 2005 he and his band visited Grenada and held a live concert.
